wdi2-TM.TAX.MRCH.BR.ZS.def: Simple mean bound rate is the unweighted average of all the lines in the tariff schedule in which bound rates have been set.
wdi2-TM.TAX.MRCH.BR.ZS.name: Bound rate, simple mean
wdi2-TM.TAX.MRCH.BR.ZS.source: World Bank staff estimates using the World Integrated Trade Solution system, based on data from World Trade Organization.
